Package net.recommenders.rival.split.splitter

Interface Summary
Splitter<U,I> Interface for the data splitter.
 

Class Summary
CrossValidationSplitter Class that splits a dataset using a cross validation technique (every interaction in the data only appears once in each test split).
RandomSplitter Class that splits a dataset randomly.
Split Main class that parses a data set and splits it according to a property file.
SplitterRunner Class that splits a dataset according to some properties.
TemporalSplitter Splitter that takes into account the timestamps in the data (older interactions are kept only in the training set).
